{
  "text": "Nanodrug release at extracellular and intracellular condition. Understanding the drug release profile in extracellular and intracellular physiological environments is a critical factor to understand the \"switch on\" mode of anti-cancer molecules to activate drug release from the nanomaterial [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "25456656"
